name: Endario Zinn
content:
Endario Zinn was a female Mirialan who worked as an agent of Chandrila Star Line. In that capacity, Zinn once recorded a video message to passengers who booked a stay on the star cruiser Halcyon in 34 ABY.
The name "Endario" previously appeared as a first and a last name of various computer-generated characters from the Star Wars: Battlefront video game series. "Zinn" similarly appeared in the game series, but also as the given name of several characters in other Star Wars fiction.
